117
00:05:33,907 --> 00:05:37,227
Even without wings, they could easily take off

118
00:05:37,227 --> 00:05:40,488
This is the reason for the peculiar shape at the back of the cars.

119
00:05:40,488 --> 00:05:44,022
These are ‘wings’ to counter the wings that planes have.

120
00:05:44,022 --> 00:05:47,092
In school, you would’ve studied that the shape of the wings of an airplane

121
00:05:47,092 --> 00:05:48,372
Aims to create a lift.

122
00:05:48,372 --> 00:05:50,416
High pressure and low pressure on either side

