124
00:05:51,981 --> 00:05:54,105
In the F1 cars, it's the opposite.

125
00:05:54,105 --> 00:05:55,877
It creates a negative lift.

126
00:05:55,877 --> 00:05:58,490
So that the cars can be pushed onto the track.

127
00:05:58,490 --> 00:06:01,581
The downforce produced is equal to 5G.

128
00:06:01,581 --> 00:06:04,224
A force of 5 times the weight of the car

129
00:06:04,224 --> 00:06:06,357
